<div class="row mbottom30">
	
	<div class="eight columns">
		<h3>Craft Boxes</h3>
		<p>Our craft boxes are aimed at children from 3 years up to 7 years, although older children (and adults) enjoy using them too.</p>
		<div id="featured">
			<%= image_tag "box-home.jpg" %>
			<%= image_tag "pirate-box-josh1.jpg" %>
			<%= image_tag "single-box-slide.jpg" %>
			<%= image_tag "pirate-box-josh2.jpg" %>
		</div>

		<p>Each craft box comes with, at least, 3 projects to complete and includes plenty of materials to keep the children busy for hours.</p>

	</div>
	
	<div class="four columns">
		<div class="panel-emph">
			<h4>Join Today</h4>
			<p>Have a look at our subscription packages and receive a great craft box, filled with craft projects, every month!</p>
			<p><%= link_to "Join", join_path, class: "button nice radius medium blue" %> </p>
		</div>
	</div>
	
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
   $(window).load(function() {
       $('#featured').orbit({
			     animation: 'fade',                  // fade, horizontal-slide, vertical-slide, horizontal-push
			     animationSpeed: 1200, 
			     pauseOnHover: true,
					 startClockOnMouseOut: true,
			     directionalNav: false,
			     fluid: true                         // or set a aspect ratio for content slides (ex: '4x3') 
			});
   });
</script>